      • step_Utick

        public void step_Utick()
        Description copied from class: C_HumanCarrier
        Activity within one time step : if a city is reached: select a new city, elaborates its path, unload rodents. If new city not reached : steps towards its current path. If vehicle speed is higher than cell size selectNextNode() is repeated several times / authors P.A.Mboup & J.Le Fur - sept.2012, rev. PAM 03.2014, JLF 10.2015
